abstract: Even conservatives used to reach across the aisle. Today, they’re too scared to try.
snippet: Even conservatives used to reach across the aisle. Today, they’re too scared to try.
lead_paragraph: When Orrin Hatch’s career in the United States Senate ends on Jan. 3, 2019, it will have spanned an audacious 42 years, or seven full terms. Assuming he completes his final term, Mr. Hatch will become the sixth-longest-serving senator ever.

abstract: Far from encouraging a return to peace talks, a pair of blunt tweets from the American president appeared to distance the Palestinians and confuse the Israelis.
snippet: Far from encouraging a return to peace talks, a pair of blunt tweets from the American president appeared to distance the Palestinians and confuse the Israelis.
lead_paragraph: JERUSALEM — If President Trump’s goal with a pair of tweets threatening to cut their funding was to compel Palestinians, one way or another, to return to peace negotiations, they appear to have had the opposite effect — and left many Israelis confused and worried as well.

abstract: A media company built on subversion and outlandishness was unable to create “a safe and inclusive workplace” for women, two of its founders acknowledge.
snippet: A media company built on subversion and outlandishness was unable to create “a safe and inclusive workplace” for women, two of its founders acknowledge.
lead_paragraph: One woman said she was riding a Ferris wheel at Coney Island after a company event when a co-worker suddenly took her hand and put it on his crotch. Another said she felt pressured into a sexual relationship with an executive and was fired after she rejected him.

snippet: The Book Review’s Help Desk columnist gives her choices of the best in self-help and how-to of 2017.

abstract: President Trump will enter his second year in office with a major legislative achievement, which Republicans will try to sell to voters in midterm elections.
snippet: President Trump will enter his second year in office with a major legislative achievement, which Republicans will try to sell to voters in midterm elections.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — President Trump ended a chaotic first year by achieving his most convincing legislative triumph on Wednesday, making good on his promise to deliver what he called a “big, beautiful” tax cut before Christmas and finally demonstrating the political power of unified Republican control in Washington.

abstract: Right before Christmas, “S.N.L.” delivered a holiday message from the White House, with President Trump (Alec Baldwin) and company decorating a tree.
snippet: Right before Christmas, “S.N.L.” delivered a holiday message from the White House, with President Trump (Alec Baldwin) and company decorating a tree.
lead_paragraph: “Saturday Night Live” got in the holiday — er, sorry — Christmas spirit in this week’s cold open, the last of the year. President Trump, performed as usual by the frowning Alec Baldwin, and the first lady, Melania Trump, played by Cecily Strong, trimmed their tree, giving them (and the show) a chance to do a little reminiscing.
